4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Course that allows students to become web development experts. The course covers building applications from scratch, teaching the most sought-after skills in the industry. It is a 16+2 week program with 3 weekly classes. No previous coding skills or advanced math are required. Students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. The course concludes with the development and presentation of a project, providing hands-on experience. Upon completion, students receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more information, visit their website. stop